#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Úvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kruler; is a very simple application, with only one aim in life. To measure "
"pixel distances on your screen. It is useful for working on layout of "
"dialogs, web pages &etc;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start &kruler;, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Applications</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Utilities</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>More Applications</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Screen Ruler</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from your "
"application menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kruler;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kruler;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kruler;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kruler;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &LMB; on the &kruler; will turn the cursor to a cross with "
"four arrows and enables you to drag &kruler; around the screen."
msgstr ""
"Kliknutím <mousebutton>levým tlačítkem myši</mousebutton> na &kruler; se "
"kurzor změní na kříž se čtyřmi šipkami a dovolí vám přetáhnout &kruler; po "
"obrazovce."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you move the mouse over &kruler;, your cursor will turn into a red "
"arrow. As you move the cursor, &kruler; will display how far from the origin "
"the cursor currently is."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can resize the ruler by moving the mouse over the handle on the left or "
"right edges of &kruler; (the top or bottom edges when it is oriented "
"vertically), holding down the &LMB; and dragging the handle."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can change the orientation in two different ways:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the &MMB; switches the ruler from vertical to horizontal orientation"
msgstr ""
"Kliknutí <mousebutton>prostředního tlačítka myši</mousebutton> přepíná mezi "
"svislou a vodorovnou orientací"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the context menu, described in the next chapter"
msgstr "Používání místní nabídky je popsáno v další kapitole."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Reference"
msgstr "Manuál pro hlavní nabídku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on the ruler will pop up a context menu, with the "
"following entries:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknutím <mousebutton>pravým tlačítkem myši</mousebutton> na pravítko, se "
"zobrazí místní nabídka, s následujícími položkami:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switches &kruler; from vertical to horizontal orientation."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scale"
msgstr "Měřítko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you set the ruler scale to <guilabel>Right to Left</"
"guilabel> (<keycap>D</keycap>), <guilabel>Center Origin</guilabel> "
"(<keycap>C</keycap>), <guilabel>Offset</guilabel> (<keycap>O</keycap>) and "
"<guilabel>Percentage</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Tato volba umožňuje nastavení pravítka <guilabel>Zprava do leva</guilabel> "
"(<keycap>D</keycap>), <guilabel>Nulu na střed</guilabel> (<keycap>C</"
"keycap>), <guilabel>Posun...</guilabel> (<keycap>O</keycap>) a "
"<guilabel>Zastoupení</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the offset via the mousewheel is also possible when holding the "
"&LMB;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opacity"
msgstr "Krytí"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu item displays a slider to change the opacity of &kruler;."
msgstr ""
"Tato položka nabídky zobrazuje posuvník, abyste mohli změnit krytí okna "
"aplikace &kruler;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Shortcuts..."
msgstr "Klávesové zkratky..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Configure Shortcut</guilabel> dialog allows you to assign "
"shortcuts to &kruler; actions, and configure the shortcuts already assigned."
msgstr ""
"Dialogové okno <guilabel>Nastavit klávesové zkratky</guilabel> umožňuje "
"přiřadit klávesové zkratky činnostem aplikace &kruler; a přenastavit již "
"přiřazené klávesové zkratky."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/config.html#shortcuts\">Shortcuts</ulink> of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Pro více informací si přečtěte část o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui."
"html#menus-help\">klávesových zkratkách</ulink> v nápovědě Základy &kde;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &kruler;..."
msgstr "Nastavit &kruler;..."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kruler;'s settings dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dialogové okno nastavení aplikace &kruler;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kruler;'s settings dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dialogové okno nastavení aplikace &kruler;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this dialog you can change the background color and font and enable the "
"tray icon."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zavřít</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Hides</action> &kruler;. It can be shown again using the icon in the "
"system tray. The context menu displays this item only when <guilabel>Show "
"tray icon</guilabel> is checked in the <link linkend=\"settings-dialog"
"\">settings dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Skrývá</action> &kruler;. Ten může být znovu zobrazen použitím ikony "
"v systémové liště. Místní nabídka zobrazuje tuto položku, pouze když je "
"zaškrtnuto <guilabel>Zobrazit ikonu v systémové liště</guilabel> v <link "
"linkend=\"settings-dialog\">dialogovém okně nastavení</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Ukončit</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kruler;"
msgstr "<action>Ukončuje</action> &kruler;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kruler; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for more "
"information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Handling"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can move the ruler using the arrow key buttons."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move the mouse cursor, and thus the indicator, by holding down &Alt; "
"and using the arrow buttons."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hold down &Shift; while doing one of those to move faster."
msgstr ""

